title: [Inking Den, Storage Hallway]
description: Stretching the length of the eastern wall, bright tiles of various hues and sizes are fitted together to create a rolling sea mosaic.  Beneath the churning waves are several wavy kelp beds, while above is a night sky displaying the tiny spheres of all four moons.  A large wrought iron ring anchored to the ceiling holds a glass-paned lantern over a curtained opening and provides ample illumination over the navy blue and gold rug-covered ground.
